Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.68,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}何処に行けば...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:19.56,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}世界と君が生命をやり直すために
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.19,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs25\an1\pos(30,65)}「Dead or alive and go」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.69,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}生きていた証だ
